###################################################################
### This is the public todo list for GWF3 and featured modules. ###
###################################################################

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

It is currently not possible to have two database instances because many GDO:: functions do a call to gdo_db().
We might want to add an optional parameter to these functions, or re-think GDO / switch to PDO.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Increase performance by not requireing a database for simple pages.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Increase performance of slow pages by using smarty templates.
Currently these pages are known to be very slow: "Forum".

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

All lang files now use %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s and so on.
This could be changed to %s %s %s %s which might be faster and is more readable.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Currently we are using Common::getGet() a lot, but Common::getGetString/Int/Array is more safe and appropiate.
Keep in mind that getGetString returns empty string by default, compared to false for getGet.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Own chat is broken (remove?)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
